Package: promptr
Title: Format and Complete Few-Shot LLM Prompts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joe", "Ornstsein", , "jornstein@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5704-2098"))
Description: The `promptr` package allows R users to format and submit few-shot prompts to OpenAI's Large Language Models (LLMs). It is designed to be particularly useful for text classification problems in the social sciences.
